      "content": "thanks. i'm curious about the \"short term\" part though. people in the coal towns are saying it's gonna be way more than just a little bump in unemployment, like it's basically the death of their local economies. do u think the bill is actually ignoring the damage it's doing to those towns, or is that just how the transition works?",
